REFINED WITH THE SIDE CHAIN IN THE TWO ALTERNATIVE
CONFORMATIONS.  PROTEIN DATA BANK ENTRIES 1L39 AND 1L40
CONTAIN COORDINATES CORRESPONDING TO THE TWO DIFFERENT
CONFORMATIONS OF GLU 144.
;
